Female (
IBSP
166771):

Carapace and chelicerae orange (
Fig. 38F
). Endites orange; labium dark orange. Sternum light orange, with darker margins, and marbled with dark pigment (
Fig. 38G
). Palps orange, gradually darkening to distal direction (
Fig. 38F‒G
